      "sectionId":"commentisfree",
      "sectionName":"Comment is free",
      "webPublicationDate":"2013-11-06T19:15:00Z",
      "webTitle":"MPs may live to regret this rash bid to neuter charities | Zoe Williams",
      "webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2013/nov/06/mps-may-regret-bid-to-neuter-charities",
