      "webPublicationDate":"2013-10-22T10:13:00Z",
      "webTitle":"Lobbying bill leaves charities and religious groups in anxious wait",
      "webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/voluntary-sector-network/2013/oct/22/lobbying-bill-charities-religious-groups",
